{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells/task-10","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 10","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Estebanu je potrebno da se predstavi tokom sastanka. Želi da vežba, pa je odlučio da napiše kratak uvod na papir. Sastanak će biti održan popodne. Pomozi Estebanu da izabere prave reči kako bi se osećao samouverenije.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pronađi tačnu reč sa liste ispod da pomogne Estebanu.</p>\n<p><strong>VAŽNO</strong>: Neke riječi se ne koriste, neke nemaju značenje u ovom kontekstu, i možeš koristiti svaku riječ <strong>samo jednom</strong>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hola</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Me llamo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Adiós</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tardes</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mañana</span>.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Ovaj kratki uvod koristi salutaciju <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hola</span>, popodnevni pozdrav <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes</span>, upotrebu imena <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Me llamo</span>, i glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span> za profesiju.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells/task-10"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK, buenas BLANK.</p>\n<p>BLANK Esteban. BLANK desarrollador.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Hola","feedback":"<p>Ovo je uobičajen način da se kaže \"Habari\" na španski.</p>"},{"answer":"tardes","feedback":"<p>Ova reč znači \"popodne\" i koristi se u pozdravima nakon popodneva.</p>"},{"answer":"Me llamo","feedback":"<p>Ovaj izraz znači \"Moje ime je\" i često se koristi za predstavljanje.</p>"},{"answer":"Soy","feedback":"<p>Ova reč znači \"Ja sam\" i koristi se pre spominjanja profesije.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":null,"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells","dashedName":"task-10","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-greetings-and-farewells","block":"es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-greetings-and-farewells/grammar-highlights","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells/task-9","id":"68c98ad382b60c54f0d4d6bf","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-greetings-and-farewells/task-10"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}